      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this Class II device assessment.",
      "rationale": "Formal input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2. Nominal input values for blood viscosity, density, and pump geometry are well characterized from published literature and manufacturer specifications. Sensitivity to input variation is addressed qualitatively."
    },
    {
