      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental data source is publicly available FDA benchmark dataset.",
      "rationale": "Formal test sample characterization is not required at MRL 2. The FDA benchmark experimental dataset provides sufficient experimental coverage for the validation activities supporting this MRL 2 Class II device assessment."
    },
    {
