      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 given direct geometry and condition matching between validation and COU.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters is not formally assessed at MRL 2. The validation geometry (FDA generic centrifugal pump) and operating conditions are sufficiently representative of the COU to support the hemolysis prediction decision without formal parameter equivalency mapping."
