    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted at MRL 2 for the CPB use context. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed and all met or exceeded their required levels. The remaining six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for this Class II device with medium model influence. The model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the centrifugal blood pump.",
